    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total stunner. This car is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it still has that fresh, showroom feel! It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. I'm looking for a smooth sale, so come grab this beauty while it lasts! You won't be disappointed! \u2728",
